        </div>
        <h3><strong>Data-Driven Partnership Decisions</strong></h3>
        <p>
          KOL partnerships can quickly drain marketing budgets when reach estimates fail to reflect actual engagement. X Bot solves this problem by providing verified data that powers smarter partnership evaluation decisions.
        </p>
        <p>
